Busy schedules, family commitments, or simply preferring privacy — many Srinagar residents now book **salon services at home** instead of waiting at a crowded salon.

Panun Kaergar offers two categories:

## Women's salon at home

- Hair styling and cuts
- Facials and skincare
- Manicure and pedicure
- Threading and waxing
- Party and bridal prep
- Mehndi for special occasions

[Book women's salon in Srinagar →](/services/womens-salon/srinagar)

## Men's salon at home

- Haircut and styling
- Beard trim and shaping
